pace":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"2685632513","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2685632513","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjY4NTYzMjUxMw==","status":"current","title":"Tpago","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":10589376},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2685632513/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2685632513","tinyui":"/x/AYATo","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2685632513","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2685632513/Tpago","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2685632513"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"321e73e5-eec9-4293-a926-46fb20c2f233\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para la iniciativa de agregar el flujo de 3DS a TPago, a cargo de <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"712020:bd6be9b3-2ff0-412b-8fb1-57e9e188f6cf\" ri:local-id=\"1f16aaa7-88e9-45ed-9404-923c140ed161\" /></ac:link> y <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" ri:local-id=\"350b650c-bbb7-46fa-8198-dbe72c8d89be\" /></ac:link> </p><p>Las horas estimadas son: <strong>422h ~ 54 d&iacute;as</strong></p><p>Fecha estimada de Inicio del desarrollo: <strong>Lunes</strong> <time datetime=\"2025-05-12\" /></p><p>Fecha estimada de entrega: <strong>Jueves</strong> <time datetime=\"2025-06-19\" /> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"1462\" data-layout=\"center\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 968.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 299.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 189.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Repositorio</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#c0b6f2\"><p>VPos Mandato Gambling - Ajustes para flujo completo/ pruebas</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#c0b6f2\"><p>vpos</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#c0b6f2\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#c0b6f2\"><p>VPos Mandato Gambling - Ajustes para flujo completo/ Peer review y correcciones/ Deploy a Staging</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#c0b6f2\"><p>vpos</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#c0b6f2\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>DDC</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>Endpoint para averiguar si se requiere 3DSec para un proceso</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>Endpoint para averiguar si se requiere 3DSec para un proceso.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>Endpoint de creaci&oacute;n de JWT para ddc</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>Tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>Endpoint de creaci&oacute;n de JWT para ddc</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>Integrar DDC form y frame en el formulario de catastro. Inlcuye: asignar input ddc_jw al form, submitear el form con target ddc_frame, obtenci&oacute;n de un cardinal_session_id al finalizar el ddc.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>Integrar DDC form y frame en el formulario pago con nueva tarjeta</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p><ac:inline-comment-marker ac:ref=\"434d5b28-6040-41af-ba56-3a8ab56b847e\">Integrar DDC form y frame en el formulario de pago con tarjeta catastrada</ac:inline-comment-marker></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffbdad\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#fff0b3\"><p>Lookup</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#fff0b3\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#fff0b3\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#fff0b3\"><p>Endpoint de lookup</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#fff0b3\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#fff0b3\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#fff0b3\"><p>Endpoint de lookup. Realizar lookup en base a cardinal_session_id y datos de la compra/catastro. Crear registro en la tabla cardinal_sessions asociado a la compra/catastro. Persistir respuesta de Lookup. Evaluar necesidad de challenge. Si hay challenge, generar JWT para llamar al endpoint del stepUpUrl.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#fff0b3\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#fff0b3\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">24hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>Challenge</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>Integrar CMPI form y frame para realizar challenge en el flujo de catastro de tarjeta</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>Integrar CMPI form y frame para realizar challenge en el flujo de pagos con tarjeta nueva</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>Integrar CMPI form y frame para realizar challenge en el flujo de pagos con tarjeta catastrada</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>Endpoint de ReturnUrl para cuando finaliza el challenge &rarr; disparar submit del form (catastro de tarjeta)</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>Endpoint de ReturnUrl para cuando finaliza el challenge &rarr; disparar submit del form (pago con tarjeta nueva)</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>Endpoint de ReturnUrl para cuando finaliza el challenge &rarr; disparar submit del form (pago con tarjeta catastrada)</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#abf5d1\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p>Authenticate</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\" /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p>Catastro de tarjeta: realizar authenticate si el flujo lo requiere, persistir respuesta de authenticate en el registro CardinalSession. Vincular la nueva UserCard al NewCardRequest.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p>Pago con tarjeta nueva: realizar authenticate si el flujo lo requiere, persistir respuesta de authenticate en el registro CardinalSession. vincular nuevo pago al CardinalSession.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p>Pago con tarjeta nueva: Si se eligi&oacute; la opci&oacute;n de catastrar nueva tarjeta, y el pago fue exitoso, catastrar sin pasar por 3DSec la nueva tarjeta en un proceso as&iacute;ncrono</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p>Pago con tarjeta catastrada: realizar authenticate si el flujo lo requiere, persistir respuesta de authenticate en el registro CardinalSession. Vincular nuevo pago al CardinalSession.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3f5ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>Enviar datos de cardinal a los endpoints de jpos de catastro y pago.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>Ajustar metodos de catastro/pago para aceptar par&aacute;metros de Cardinal.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>external-services</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>Crear y editar modelos con sus respectivas migraciones:<br />- NewCardRequest (nuevo)<br />- UserCards<br />- CardinalAcceptedCards (nuevo)<br />- CardinalSessions (nuevo)</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>Limitar catastros a un m&aacute;ximo de 5 tarjetas activas y habilitadas no retroactivo.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>Pago con nueva tarjeta: usuario logueado. deshabilitar checkbox de guardar tarjeta si el usuario ya alcanz&oacute; el limite de tarjetas</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>Pago con nueva tarjeta: usuario logueado. Hacer nueva operaci&oacute;n para consultar numero de tarjetas activas. </p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>Agregar configuraciones de credenciales y flags de Cardinal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>bancard-configurations</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>Agregar configuraciones de credenciales y flags de Cardinal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>Pagos con tarjeta nueva: Validar resultado del proceso kount. Comenzar 3DSec s&oacute;lo en caso de que kount sea exitoso o no haya sucedido.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>tpago-portal</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>Integrar servicio de tokenizacion para catastros <code>/bancard/util/tarjeta_token</code> </p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p>payment-link-service</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#b3d4ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Salida a Staging</p><ul><li><p>Integraci&oacute;n de los flujos</p></li><li><p>Creaci&oacute;n y correci&oacute;n de PRs</p></li><li><p>Pruebas locales</p></li><li><p>Armado de ramas</p></li><li><p>Deploy a STG</p></li><li><p>Pruebas iniciales en STG</p></li></ul></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">32hs</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">368h</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">54h</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">422h</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3897492453"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":91990885},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3897492453/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3897492453/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3897492453/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3897492453/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3897492453","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3897492453/3DS+en+TPago+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3897492453","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3897492453","tinyui":"/x/5QNP6","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}